{
  "id": 5157805733183488,
  "name": "CSS Gap Decorations",
  "summary": "CSS Gap Decorations enables styling of gaps in container layouts like Grid and Flexbox, similar to ‘column-rule’ in multicol layout. This feature is highly requested by web authors who must use hacks to style the gaps in Grid and Flexbox layouts today.",
